    "FishHeroDes" : "!16h! Thank you to the heroes who took part in our first test and gave us so much valuable advice. With your help, our game has been greatly improved!\n      Here is a list of those incredible heroes:",
    "FreeScene_ConditionDes" : "!16i! Difficulty",
    "FreeScene_ContentConditionDes" : "!16j! The difficulty determines the <color=#df840e>available citizens</color> and <color=#df840e>resources on map</color> at the start of the game. Temperature and food production from structures will also drop on higher difficulties.",
    "FreeScene_ContentDisasterDes" : "!16k! Disasters may lead to devastating results, but much of their destruction can be avoided with proper planning.",
    "FreeScene_ContentHillDes" : "!16l! Mountains are rich in mineral resources, but may create problems for town planning.",
    "FreeScene_ContentLokeSizeDes" : "!16m! Lakes are bodies of water surrounded by land. Suitable for water-related development.",
    "FreeScene_ContentPlotDes" : "!16n! Story Mode: You can experience the rise and fall of the settlement on a preset map by completing tasks when enabled. You can build freely on the map if you disable it.",
    "FreeScene_ContentShaheDes" : "!16o! Sandbox mode is for players who are already familiar with this game.",
    "SpecialBuild_Tip" : "!16p! Special Structures: Rubik's Cube and Goof-off Hero will now appear in Blueprint toolbar when enabled.",
    "FreeScene_ContentStoneDes" : "!16q! Ore is necessary for several industries. They are non-renewable resources.",
    "FreeScene_ContentTerrainDes" : "!16r! Each map size offers a different experience. If you are new to the game we advise that you use the recommended map size.",
    "FreeScene_ContentTerrainSeedDes" : "!16s! Map seeds create random differences in the map's mountains and rivers.",
    "FreeScene_ContentTreeNumDes" : "!16t! Vegetation provides primary resources like wood and food. Plants are renewable. Maps with a high vegetation density are more rich in resources.",
    "FreeScene_ContentWaterNumDes" : "!16u! River branches increase the water area. Works better with wide rivers.",
    "FreeScene_ContentWaterSizeDes" : "!16v! Wider rivers mean larger water areas but smaller land areas.",
    "FreeScene_ContentWeatherDes" : "!16w! The climate has an impact on both the citizens and the crops. Cold weather makes the game more difficult.",
    "FreeScene_DisasterDes" : "!16x! Disaster",
    "FreeScene_FindLivePos" : "!16y! Discover new settlements!",
