    "LogState_InfoDes_39" : "!1tm! Lack of Laborer！",
    "LogState_InfoDes_4" : "!1tn! There are citizens without houses to live in who can only recover stamina by loafing around. They can only get warm at other citizens' homes and get food and water from the warehouse. Homeless citizens cannot have children.",
