    "Technology_Content_1" : "!2m9! Unlock <color=#df840e>Mill</color> and <color=#df840e>Water Mill</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_10" : "!2ma! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Advanced Bakery</color> which can produce food for travel.",
    "Technology_Content_100" : "!2mb! Herdsmen can acquire <color=#df840e>dried animal dung</color> through daily cleaning.",
    "Technology_Content_101" : "!2mc! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Composting Plant</color>. Fertilizer is made from Dried Dung, which is produced by pasture animals. The resource spot of Fertile Soil will be created in the center of the building, providing a 50% production buff for agricultural structures within the range.",
    "Technology_Content_102" : "!2md! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Farm</color> and the <color=#df840e>Standard Farm</color>, which can be fertilized to boost yield.",
    "Technology_Content_103" : "!2me! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Grove</color>, which can be fertilized to boost yield.",
    "Technology_Content_104" : "!2mf! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Plantation</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_105" : "!2mg! You received free <color=#df840e>Hay Seeds</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_106" : "!2mh! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Fodder Factory</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_107" : "!2mi! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Eco-pasture</color>, where you can use fodder to accelerate animal growth.",
    "Technology_Content_108" : "!2mj! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Fishpond</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_109" : "!2mk! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Corral</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_11" : "!2ml! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Apiary</color> which can produce <color=#df840e>honey</color> and <color=#df840e>beeswax</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_110" : "!2mm! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Estate</color>, which combines production, housing, storage, and markets.",
    "Technology_Content_112" : "!2mn! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Fishing Boat</color>. Fishing boats have a <color=#df840e>stable yield</color> and do not affect each other.",
    "Technology_Content_113" : "!2mo! Unlock the recipe for making <color=#df840e>fish nets</color> at the Knitting Workshop.",
    "Technology_Content_114" : "!2mp! Unlock the recipe for making <color=#df840e>fish nets</color> at the Knitting Workshop.",
    "Technology_Content_115" : "!2mq! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Fishing Port</color>, where you can use <color=#df840e>fishing nets</color> to acquire large amounts of fish products.",
    "Technology_Content_123" : "!2mr! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Hospital</color>. It grants <color=#df840e>Health</color> bonuses by consuming high-grade items, and can greatly increase the curing speed of <color=#df840e>Tuberculosis</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_117" : "!2ms! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Tavern</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_118" : "!2mt! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Theater</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_119" : "!2mu! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Civic Square</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_12" : "!2mv! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Sugar Workshop</color>, <color=#df840e>Cannery</color> and <color=#df840e>Jam Workshop</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_120" : "!2mw! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Nursery</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_204" : "!2mx! Unlock <color=#df840e>Cathedral</color>, a kind of structure capable of granting extra <color=#df840e>happiness bonus</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_122" : "!2my! Doctors can <color=#df840e>go out to treat patients</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_43" : "!2mz! Unlock structure <color=#df840e>Marquee</color>, can be placed out side marketplaces' control zones, cannot be upgraded.",
    "Technology_Content_124" : "!2n0! Increase the life expectancy of all citizens by <color=#df840e>10-20 years</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_125" : "!2n1! Medical care has been improved, which increases the life expectancy of all citizens by <color=#df840e>10-20 years</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_126" : "!2n2! The <color=#df840e>Storage Yard</color> can now store more items.",
    "Technology_Content_127" : "!2n3! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Cellar</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_128" : "!2n4! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Storage Center</color> and <color=#df840e>Mountain Warehouse</color>.",
    "Technology_Content_129" : "!2n5! Unlock the <color=#df840e>Warehouse</color>, which has a greater storage capacity than the Storage Yard. Unlock the <color=#df840e>Small Warehouse</color>.",
