    "EventLog_1126" : "!3lk! Event - the Arrival of a Sommelier (click to trigger)",
    "EventName_1126" : "!3ll! The Arrival of a Sommelier",
    "EventDes_1126" : "!3lm! A self-proclaimed master sommelier came to your town and disbelieved people in the town could produce fine wine.\n      'You must be talking big. I dare you to show me the wine in your warehouse?'",
    "EventChoose_1126_1" : "!3ln! Show the premium wine in warehouse. (Need {0} in stock)",
    "ActiveEvent_Des_11261" : "!3lo! 'Didn't expect there are people here who appreciate fine wine!'\n      The sommelier was deeply touched and gifted his whiskey collection to you.",
    "EventChoose_1126_2" : "!3lp! Lack of wine in stock, you missed the opportunity to impress the sommelier.",
    "EventLog_1127" : "!3lq! Event - The Joining of Scholars (click to trigger)",
    "EventName_1127" : "!3lr! The Joining of Scholars",
    "EventDes_1127" : "!3ls! Around twenty or so young scholars passed through the town.\n      'Based on our measurements of paper use in this town, you have a strong desire to spread knowledge. We would like to join this academic place.'",
    "EventChoose_1127_1" : "!3lt! Accept them.",
    "EventChoose_1127_2" : "!3lu! Refuse them.",
    "EventLog_1128" : "!3lv! Event - Fashion Show (click to trigger)",
    "EventName_1128" : "!3lw! Fashion Show",
    "EventDes_1128" : "!3lx! The town's clothing industry is booming, and our officials want to invite famous designers to hold a fashion show here. However, the designers have one requirement:",
    "EventChoose_1128_1" : "!3ly! We'd love to hold a fashion show if there are {0} stocked in your town.",
    "ActiveEvent_Des_11281" : "!3lz! The designers were impressed by the citizens' exquisite clothing, and so they shared a batch of their well-designed gowns.",
    "EventLog_1129" : "!3m0! Even - Nostalgia (click to trigger)",
    "EventName_1129" : "!3m1! Nostalgia",
    "EventDes_1129" : "!3m2! As time went on, some citizens wanted to emigrate to other cities, and some immigrants wanted to go back to their former homeland. They left the town but may come back to visit in the future!",
    "EventChoose_1129_1" : "!3m3! 20 citizens decided to leave.",
    "EventLog_1130" : "!3m4! Event - Refugees (click to trigger)",
    "EventName_1130" : "!3m5! Refugees",
    "EventDes_1130" : "!3m6! 'We are starving! Could you offer us some food?'\n      There were more than 20 refugees from famine areas trying to get relief here. If we had enough food, maybe we could help them. Otherwise, our citizens may have to compete with refugees for food.",
    "EventChoose_1130_1" : "!3m7! Accept the refugees. (Need {0} in stock)",
    "EventChoose_1130_2" : "!3m8! Refuse them.",
    "EventLog_1131" : "!3m9! Event - Skill Honing (click to trigger)",
    "EventName_1131" : "!3ma! Skill Honing",
    "EventDes_1131" : "!3mb! Some artisans from other places passed through the town and wanted to engage in collaborative learning with the locals.\n      'Everything here is so beautifully made! Your craftsmanship is very advanced! Can you show me your tools?'",
    "EventChoose_1131_1" : "!3mc! Hone their skills by collaborative learning. (Need: {0} in stock)",
    "ActiveEvent_Des_11311" : "!3md! Through collaborative learning, the local artisans acquired more practical tool usage techniques. The output in all kinds of workshops will increase by 20% in the next year.",
    "EventLog_1132" : "!3me! Event - Foodie's Adventure Team (click to trigger)",
    "EventName_1132" : "!3mf! Foodie's Adventure Team",
    "EventDes_1132" : "!3mg! A gourmet named Foodie came to the town with his adventure team. You wonder what food in town can appeal to them?",
    "EventChoose_1132_1" : "!3mh! Invite them to taste the local cuisine. (require {0} in stock)",
    "ActiveEvent_Des_11321" : "!3mi! The local cuisine impressed them, who then shared many recipes with the citizens.",
