    "Item_Des_130002" : "!3ub! A paper note found from lanterns. Riddles and wishes are written on it. This event item can only be obtained during event time.",
    "Item_Des_130003" : "!3uc! With money inside as an amulet. In Eastern cultures, giving this money to children protects them from evil and danger throughout the year. This event item increases citizens' inventory and can only be produced during event time.",
    "Item_Des_130004" : "!3ud! Food made from <color=#df840e>Rice</color> at the <color=#df840e>Mill</color>, which is called 'Nian Gao' in Chinese, meaning life would be better over the next year. Event item, only can be made during the event period.",
    "Item_Des_130005" : "!3ue! Food made from <color=#df840e>Flour</color> and <color=#df840e>Meat Chop</color> at the <color=#df840e>Gourmet Shop</color>, which can bring good luck over the next year. Event item, only can be made during the event period.",
    "Item_Des_130006" : "!3uf! Food made from <color=#df840e>Rice</color> and <color=#df840e>Sugar</color> at the <color=#df840e>Mill</color>, which is called 'Tang Yuan' in Chinese, conveying a wish of family reunion and happiness. Event item, only can be made during the event period.",
    "Item_Des_130007" : "!3ug! A wine made from <color=#df840e>Herbs</color> and <color=#df840e>Water</color> at the <color=#df840e>Winery</color>. It improves citizens' <color=#df840e>Health</color> and helps them <color=#df840e>be immune to the plague</color> for a certain period. This event item can only be produced during event time.",
    "Item_Des_130008" : "!3uh! Low-power explosives made from <color=#df840e>coal</color> and <color=#df840e>paper</color> at the <color=#df840e>Fuel Factory</color>, which will make a loud noise when lit. What a blast! Event item, only can be made during the event period.",
    "Building_Name_ID_11006" : "!3ui! Lantern",
    "Building_Des_ID_11006" : "!3uj! <color=#df840e>Decorative</color> structure that can be placed in the town. <color=#df840e>Provides lighting</color>.",
    "Building_Name_ID_11007" : "!3uk! Firework",
    "Building_Des_ID_11007" : "!3ul! Can build more than one. Citizens will set off all the fireworks when lighting one of them. It takes three months to prepare new fireworks.",
    "BuildInfo_Fireworks" : "!3um! Light",
    "BuildInfo_FireworksTip" : "!3un! Preparing fireworks:",
    "Building_Name_ID_11008" : "!3uo! Rui Beast Plaza",
    "Building_Des_ID_11008" : "!3up! Plaza guarded by five Rui Beast statues, symbolizing peace and happiness. Can set off the firecrackers every 5 years to celebrate the festival.",
    "BuildInfo_AnimalSquare" : "!3uq! Set off",
