    "SpringEvent_1" : "!3us! Paste up 'Fu'",
    "SpringEvent_2" : "!3ut! Event - Paste Up 'Fu' (click to trigger)",
    "SpringEvent_3" : "!3uu! The New Year arrived and citizens were going to paste up the Chinese character \"Fu\" on the door to show their wishes in next year. How are they supposed to paste it up?",
    "SpringEvent_4" : "!3uv! Paste it up normally.",
    "SpringEvent_5" : "!3uw! Paste up it upside down.",
    "SpringEvent_6" : "!3ux! An old man came out to stop the citizens from pasting the character 'Fu'.\n      'Oh this young man, the Chinese character 'Fu' should be pasted upside down, which means happiness is flowing down into you thus we could have good fortune in the New Year!'",
    "SpringEvent_7" : "!3uy! Citizens put up the Chinese character 'Fu' and prepared a lot of food to celebrate the Lunar New Year.",
    "SpringEvent_8" : "!3uz! The character 'Fu' is pasted upside down, that is, 'happiness is flowing down into you' in the New Year!",
    "SpringEvent_9" : "!3v0! Nian, the New Year Beast",
    "SpringEvent_10" : "!3v1! A fierce man-eating monster 'Nian' came to the town. It was told that this monster will slaughter people and livestock, so how are you going to deal with it?",
    "SpringEvent_11" : "!3v2! Feed it with food.",
    "SpringEvent_12" : "!3v3! Scare it away with firecrackers. (Need: {0})",
    "SpringEvent_13" : "!3v4! The hungry monster ate a lot of food and killed some villagers before leaving.",
    "SpringEvent_14" : "!3v5! The explosion of firecrackers and the red paper seemed to startle the monster. It quickly ran away.",
    "SpringEvent_15" : "!3v6! Yuanxiao Lanterns",
    "SpringEvent_16" : "!3v7! Citizens were attracted by the beautiful lanterns on the river and found paper notes with riddles and New Year wishes hanging from them.",
    "SpringEvent_17" : "!3v8! Try to solve the lantern riddles.",
    "SpringEvent_18" : "!3v9! Collect the paper notes with riddles.",
    "SpringEvent_19" : "!3va! Some citizens managed to guess the lantern riddles and won a reward!",
    "SpringEvent_20" : "!3vb! Lunar New Year Gift",
