    "Policy_01_Des" : "!6bg! Education is critical to society. This policy determines the education direction of the town.",
    "Policy_02_Des" : "!6bh! \"The life of the dead is placed on the memories of the living.\" The policy determines how the dead are buried.",
    "Policy_03_Des" : "!6bi! Proper housing is the basis of a healthy society. The policy will determine housing density.",
    "Policy_04_Des" : "!6bj! Water is the source of all life. The policy will regulate how citizens use water resources.",
    "Policy_05_Des" : "!6bk! Agriculture is the foundation of an economy. The policy regulates food import and export prices.",
    "Policy_06_Des" : "!6bl! Crops are a blessing of nature. The policy regulates how fields will be harvested.",
    "Policy_07_Des" : "!6bm! We value communication and trade among factions. The policy will determine the direction of trade in the town.",
    "Policy_08_Des" : "!6bn! Water is the silk road of trade, and the policy determines the trading mode at the dock.",
    "Policy_09_Des" : "!6bo! The quality has effects on prices. The policy determines the direction of the manufacture in the town.",
    "Policy_10_Des" : "!6bp! Many products are processed in the town, but the labor force is limited. The policy determines the production of various products in the town.",
    "Policy_11_Des" : "!6bq! Industrial structure affects town development in every way. The policy determines the town's focus on different industries.",
    "Policy_12_Des" : "!6br! Welcome new faces or shut the door to them? The policy determines whether immigrants will be accepted.",
    "Policy_13_Des" : "!6bs! Beliefs give people strength and hope. The policy determines whether religions will be encouraged or not.",
