    "Policy_01_Options_01_Des" : "!6d9! The town will not focus on any educational direction.",
    "Policy_01_Options_02_Des" : "!6da! Science and technology are a primary productive force. Town education will focus more on science education.",
    "Policy_01_Options_03_Des" : "!6db! The body is the temple of the soul. The town education will focus more on physical education.",
    "Policy_02_Options_01_Des" : "!6dc! \"Ashes to ashes, dust to dust.\" Inhumation will be adopted in the town.",
    "Policy_02_Options_02_Des" : "!6dd! Water gives life. River burial is the beginning of spiritual rebirth. River burial will be adopted in the town.",
    "Policy_02_Options_03_Des" : "!6de! The last flame of life. Cremation will be adopted in the town, which can proceed in the Crematorium.",
    "Policy_03_Options_01_Des" : "!6df! The town will adopt the current housing policy.",
    "Policy_03_Options_02_Des" : "!6dg! Distance produces beauty. Low-Density Housing Policy will be adopted in the town.",
    "Policy_03_Options_03_Des" : "!6dh! Land is a finite resource. To make as much use of land as possible, High-Density Housing Policy will be adopted in the town.",
    "Policy_04_Options_01_Des" : "!6di! Citizens may be allowed to drink dirty river water, but doing so may put them at a high risk of contracting diseases.",
    "Policy_04_Options_02_Des" : "!6dj! Citizens are forbidden to use and drink dirty river water directly.",
    "Policy_05_Options_01_Des" : "!6dk! The town will not intervene in trading.",
    "Policy_05_Options_02_Des" : "!6dl! The price of importing and exporting food will be cheaper.",
    "Policy_05_Options_03_Des" : "!6dm! The price of importing and exporting food will be more expensive.",
    "Policy_06_Options_01_Des" : "!6dn! Every grain is precious. Farmers will collect the crops for storage as they are reaped.",
    "Policy_06_Options_02_Des" : "!6do! Organized land farming brings greater efficiency. Farmers will first reap all crops at once and then collect them for storage.",
    "Policy_06_Options_03_Des" : "!6dp! Besides crops, other things in the field can also be used. Farmers will collect grain straws and bean straws.",
    "Policy_07_Options_01_Des" : "!6dq! The town will maintain regular communication and trade with the factions.",
    "Policy_07_Options_02_Des" : "!6dr! No town can produce everything all alone. The town will strengthen communication and trade with other factions.",
    "Policy_08_Options_01_Des" : "!6ds! The dock remains in the current trading mode.",
    "Policy_08_Options_02_Des" : "!6dt! Trade brings broader choices. The dock will switch to Ordering Mode.",
    "Policy_08_Options_03_Des" : "!6du! Trade should be a win-win situation, not a zero-sum game. The dock will have more merchant ships stop by.",
    "Policy_09_Options_01_Des" : "!6dv! The town will remain in its current production pattern.",
    "Policy_09_Options_02_Des" : "!6dw! Where quality is job number one, the town will make efforts to improve the quality of certain products.",
    "Policy_09_Options_03_Des" : "!6dx! Low quality and low prices may provide short-term benefits. The town will shorten the production period of certain products.",
    "Policy_10_Options_01_Des" : "!6dy! The town will remain in the current processing pattern.",
    "Policy_10_Options_02_Des" : "!6dz! Meat is a healthy nutrition source. The town will focus more on meat processing.",
    "Policy_10_Options_03_Des" : "!6e0! Alcohol can comfort lost souls sometimes. The town will focus more on beverage processing.",
    "Policy_10_Options_04_Des" : "!6e1! Fancy trade goods worth more Silver Coins. The town will focus more on trade goods processing.",
    "Policy_10_Options_05_Des" : "!6e2! Decorative and durable construction materials are always desirable. The town will focus more on construction materials processing.",
    "Policy_11_Options_01_Des" : "!6e3! The town's industrial structure will remain unchanged.",
    "Policy_11_Options_02_Des" : "!6e4! Protecting the environment is our duty. The industrialization of the town will be more environmentally friendly.",
    "Policy_11_Options_03_Des" : "!6e5! The processing industry makes citizens' lives more convenient. The town will focus more on the processing industry.",
    "Policy_11_Options_04_Des" : "!6e6! Trading brings prosperity. The town will focus more on trading.",
    "Policy_12_Options_01_Des" : "!6e7! Manually decide whether to accept immigrants when they arrived.",
    "Policy_12_Options_02_Des" : "!6e8! What we will go through together in the future can bond us together. The town will receive all immigrants.",
    "Policy_12_Options_03_Des" : "!6e9! The peace and stability of the town are precious to everyone. The town will reject all immigrants to avoid uncertainty.",
    "Policy_13_Options_01_Des" : "!6ea! The town will remain in its current state.",
    "Policy_13_Options_02_Des" : "!6eb! We should leave ourselves time to think, reflect and be grateful in this busy world. The town will encourage religious activities.",
