    "Building_Name_ID_4110" : "!711! Bandit Camp",
    "Building_Des_ID_4110" : "!712! Bandits will be dispatched to invade the town and plunder <color=#df840e>Silver Coins</color>. They will attack citizens and buildings within their Bandit Camps' range. Within Bandit Camps' range, <color=#df840e>construction, digging, and filling will be unable to proceed</color>.",
    "Item_Name_110401" : "!713! Iron Shield",
